[According to the above report, there have now been a total of 68 500 cases of confirmed COVID-19 reported from China, representing an increase of 2018 cases in the past 24 hours, of which 1843 (91.3%) were in Hubei. In addition, there were 142 deaths reported of which 110 (97.9%) were in Hubei. No additional cases were reported from Hong Kong, Macau, or Taiwan.

