[5] Selected media reports of transmission outside of mainland China
A. Japanese cruise ship, USA citizens to be airlifted 16 Feb 2020
Date: Sat 15 Feb 2020
Source: NHK World [edited]
https://www3.nhk.or.jp/nhkworld/en/news/20200216_09/


The US State Department has chartered an airplane to evacuate hundreds of American citizens on a quarantined cruise ship anchored off the Japanese city of Yokohama. The US Embassy in Tokyo says the plane will arrive in Japan on Sunday [16 Feb 2020] evening. The American passengers and crew on the Diamond Princess will leave the ship and fly back to the United States as soon as preparations are complete.

Of the approximately 2600 passengers, 416 are Americans, 2nd only in number to the Japanese passengers. There are also 12 US crewmembers onboard. Japanese authorities say more than 280 passengers on the ship have been confirmed to be infected.

According to an email the US Embassy sent to the American passengers and crew onboard, those who decide to return to the US will have to remain in quarantine for an additional 14 days.

Meanwhile, another private-sector ferry has joined Japan's Self-Defense Forces in efforts to provide support for people onboard the Diamond Princess. The ferry serves as a 2nd base for about 150 SDF personnel engaged in such tasks as disinfecting the interior of the cruise ship. Japan's Defense Ministry is also calling up medical reservists to give support to those who come out of quarantine.

--
Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Another media report in Japanese submitted by ProMED-mail Rapporteur Kunihiko Iizuka mentions that in the past 24 hours there were 67 newly confirmed cases on the cruise ship in quarantine in Yokahama, bringing the total number of confirmed infected individuals associated with the cruise ship (passengers and crew) to 285.

The passengers being repatriated to the USA will undergo an additional 14 days in quarantine, during which continued testing will be done. One suspects other countries may start repatriating their citizens as well. A massive undertaking on all sides. - Mod.MPP]

